{
  "chapter": 314,
  "chapter_summary": "本章以寇仲与宋玉致在码头依依惜别开篇，寇仲向宋玉致倾诉对争天下的执着与对她的深情，表明即使前路艰险也不会放弃远大目标。随后镜头转向徐子陵所在的乌江帮船只，阴癸派的\"恶僧\"法难和\"艳尼\"常真强行登船追捕韩泽南夫妇。徐子陵以\"弓辰春\"身份出手，以大金刚不动轮印等精妙武学轻松击败两人，但担心引来阴癸派更厉害的高手。韩泽南一家趁夜偷偷下船逃走，徐子陵无奈叹息。寇仲在船上独自练刀，经宋缺指点后刀道修为突飞猛进，达至\"意即刀，刀即意\"的人刀合一境界。回到舱内，雷九指与林朗谈论赌术与因如阁赌会，公良寄则向徐子陵求助，讲述被骗棍赖朝贵骗光家产的遭遇，雷九指表示到九江后顺道收拾此人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "此地一别，不知是否尚能与致致有再见之日。\n\n假若我在关中寻不到杨公宝藏，我根本没有本钱去和李小子争天下，亦不会让你嫁我；即使真的得到杨公宝藏，跟李小子的实力相比，我仍是输多赢少的劣局。\n\n因为战争并非以钱财多寡来决定胜负，否则杨广不会失天下。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你是不应该来的，事而至此，玉致还有甚么话说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "事既至此，致致还不能和我说两句知心话吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "爹是明知不可为而为，所以才不肯直接派兵助你。\n\n李阀的声势与日俱增，你还在为杨公宝库痴人做梦。好啦！\n\n假设真给你寻得宝藏，你又怎样把东西运离李阀的地头？\n\n少帅啊！理性点好吗？算人家求你吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "不要看我爱嘻嘻哈哈的，一副薄皮无赖的样子，但我对致致的爱却是此生不渝的，致致定会怪我为争天下舍你而去。\n\n固然我现在已是泥足深陷，难以言退。但真正的原因，是男儿必须为自己确立一个远大的目标，然后永不言悔地朝这目标迈进，不计成败得失。\n\n子陵和我的分别，只在于目标的差异。且看看你身边的人吧！\n\n有那一个是具正快乐和满足的？我们唯一能做的事，就是苦中作乐！\n\n于平凡中找寻真趣，已与我寇仲无缘。只有在大时代的惊天骇浪中奋斗挣扎，恐惧着下一刻会遭没顶之祸，才可使我感受到自己的价值和存在。\n\n现在我只能在自己劣势的环境中，尽量做得最好，在江湖中作三两人间的争雄斗胜，再不能使我动心，只有千军万马决胜于沙场之上，那种胜败才能令人倾倒。\n\n我本是个一无所有的人，也不怕再变为一无所有，但只要我知道致致的心曾向我，寇仲已可不负此生啦。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_han_ze_nan",
      "text": "韩兄勿要出去，一切由我来应付。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "雷兄也不要露脸。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ze_nan",
      "speaker_name": "韩泽南",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弓兄千万不可卷入此事中，弓兄或者不会把这两个人放在眼内，但他们出身的家派，却是非同小可，缠上后除非死掉，否则休想有安乐日子过。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "一个是'恶僧'法难，另一个是'艳尼'常真，从没人知道他们的出身来历的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fa_nan",
      "speaker_name": "法难",
      "listener": "char_hong_xiao_shang",
      "text": "洪小裳你今次插翼难飞，若再不乖乖的随我们回去，我们便要大开杀戒。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_xiao_shang",
      "speaker_name": "洪小裳",
      "listener": "char_han_ze_nan",
      "text": "南哥珍重，好好照顾杰儿。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_xiao_shang",
      "speaker_name": "洪小裳",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "大恩不言谢，弓爷请送他们到安全地点去。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ze_nan",
      "speaker_name": "韩泽南",
      "listener": "char_hong_xiao_shang",
      "text": "要死就死在一块儿，我们永远不会分开。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_han_ze_nan",
      "text": "韩兄和嫂夫人请放心。法难常真乃祝玉妍的喽罗走狗，本人知道得一清二楚，更清楚自己惹上的是那一类的麻烦。\n\n待我去把他们收拾后，回来再和韩兄和嫂夫人商量下一步该怎么走吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弓爷请为我乌江帮主持个公道。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lin_lang",
      "text": "此事全由我揽到身上，林香主千万别惹上身，快着各兄弟收起兵器。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天的事，我乌江帮再不插手，收起兵器。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fa_nan",
      "speaker_name": "法难",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "来者何人？是否想代人出头送死？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "常真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "是否因那条像毒虫般难看的疤痕累得没女人欢喜，所以活得不耐烦啦？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_fa_nan",
      "text": "少说废话，有种的就不要夹尾巴落荒溜掉。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "常真",
      "listener": "char_fa_nan",
      "text": "师兄听过这么大言不惭的话吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "常真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "让奴家先陪你玩两招吧！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhen",
      "text": "给我有那么远就滚那么远，否则莫怪我大开杀戒。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "常真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "好！今天算你狠！不过你已惹上天大麻烦，很快你就知甚么叫后悔。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "他们都是好人，可能不想连累我们才这么一走了之吧！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "早已连累，只有希望他们吉人天相。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "有人见到他们从船头偷偷下船，沿江而逃，那段路很不好走。\n\n他们真蠢，有弓爷照拂他们，还有甚么好怕的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_lin_lang",
      "text": "巴东郡有没有像样的赌场？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "要赌当然最好到九江的因如阁，不要说大江南北的赌客趋之若骛，连不爱赌的人都要去见识一下，且现在正是因如阁一年一度的赌会举行的时刻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "我们在这里只有个许时辰，那够时间去赌呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我只是顺口问问，只要时间足够，我们泊到那里就赌到那里，否则你那来练习的机会。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "要赌还不容易，船上赌具一应俱全，就让我们玩两手如阿。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_lin_lang",
      "text": "怎好意思赢林香主辛苦赚来的钱，到郑郡后我们三个就结伴去赌个天昏地暗，无论嬴多少都分作三份，保证林香主回乌江后可起大屋纳美妾。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "既然这么容易嬴钱，老哥为何又要奔波劳碌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_liang_ji",
      "speaker_name": "公良寄",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弓爷可否借一步说话？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_gong_liang_ji",
      "text": "入房再说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_liang_ji",
      "speaker_name": "公良寄",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小人复姓公良，小名寄，乃清化郡人。\n\n今趟到九江去，是想收回一笔欠账，若弓爷肯出手帮忙，我愿分一半给弓爷，唉！\n\n若收不到这笔账，我也不知怎办才好。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_gong_liang_ji",
      "text": "究意是甚么一回事，公良兄请详细道来，但千万不可有任何隐瞒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_liang_ji",
      "speaker_name": "公良寄",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "事情是这样的，我们公良家数代相传都是做药材生意，五个月前一个叫贾充的人来向我们订下大批名贵药材，讲明以黄金交易。\n\n于是我们遂往各地搜罗，集齐后一手交货，一手收金。\n\n岂知当时明明是金锭，回来后全变作石子，才知受骗。\n\n贾充其实是假充。为了付药材的欠账，我已是倾家荡产，变得一无所有。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_gong_liang_ji",
      "text": "他既是骗子，怎会让你知道他住在九江？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_liang_ji",
      "speaker_name": "公良寄",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我也不知自己是好运道还是霉运当头，得一个江湖朋友告诉我这人是九江著名的骗棍外号'点石成金'的赖朝贵，弓爷请给小人主持公道。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "赖朝贵不但是大骗棍，还是个嫖赌饮吹样样皆精的流氓，到九江时我们顺道把他收拾吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 314,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 316
    }
  ],
